<sect2>
<title>Installer <application>Imlib</application></title>

<para>Installez <application>Imlib</application> en lançant les commandes
suivantes:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>./configure --prefix=/usr --sysconfdir=/etc/imlib &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>
